1. pip install fast api  (install fast api)

2. pip install uvicorn (install fast api server)

3. python -m venv venv   (create virtual environment)

4. .\venv\Scripts\Activate (activate virtual environment)

5. pip freeze > requirements.txt (take notes for packages used in this project)

6. python run.py (run the fastapi application)

7. uvicorn app.main:app --reload (reload the fastapi application)

8. pip install mysql-connector-python sqlalchemy (install mySQL db packages)